Subject: [PATCH v4 4/9] ASoC: mediatek: mt8188: refine APLL control
Date:   Wed, 10 May 2023 11:55:21 +0800
Message-ID: <20230510035526.18137-5-trevor.wu@mediatek.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.18.0
